    {
      "id": "detailed_1_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_1",
      "description": "This vehicle is in absolute mint condition and presents exactly as it did when it first left the showroom. The exterior paint is entirely flawless with a deep, mirror-like finish, and there are no scratches, chips, or imperfections of any kind. Inside, the cabin is in pristine condition, with leather that remains supple and all features functioning perfectly. This is a rare opportunity to own a collector-grade example that has been meticulously maintained and garage-kept its entire life.",
